# PAM service for the MurOS web UI.
#
# The web UI authenticates operators against the exact same Linux account
# stack used by local login and SSH, so a single credential set covers
# both the UI and shell access. We reuse the distribution common-auth /
# common-account includes (pam_unix against /etc/shadow, plus any site
# policy already layered there).
@include common-auth
@include common-account
